課程概述 Course Description
       講述以不同的數學及物理模式來定量藥品在體內的吸收，分佈及代謝以選擇最適合的給藥方式達到最大療效最小副作用之目的 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    講述以不同的數學及物理模式來定量藥品在體內的吸收，分佈及代謝以選擇最適合的給藥方式達到最大療效最小副作用之目的。    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Introduction of clinical pharmacokinetics2Compartmental model3Extravascular dose4Constant-rate regimens5Overview of drug metabolism6Metabolism＆urinary kinetics7Multiple-dose regimens8Physiologic factors affecting drug absorption9Physiologic factors affecting drug distribution10Physiologic factors affecting drug elimination11Drug interaction12Integration of physiologic factors with kinetics13Statistics in bioavailability and bioequivalence14studies(PK homework discussion)15Non-linear pharmacokinetics and pharmacogenetics16TDM17Final Exam18  

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


